''' {{ill|Tsuchimikado Hisanaga|ja|土御門久脩|12=draft|12=draft}}
''' Daughter: Married to {{ill|Kanjūji Harutoyo|ja|勧修寺晴豊|12=draft|12=draft}}

=== Descendants===
The male-line descendants of {{ill|Abe no Seimei|ja|安倍晴明|12=draft|12=draft}} through Tsuchimikado Arinaga have largely been lost. Notably, the {{ill|Kurahashi family|ja|倉橋家|12=draft|12=draft}} (a cadet branch of the Abe clan) and the {{ill|Kanjūji family|ja|勧修寺家|12=draft|12=draft}} trace their lineage through Arinaga's children and subsequent marriages. The family line continued through daughter’s descendants and their connections to prominent aristocratic families, including the {{ill|Imperial House of Japan|ja|皇室|12=draft|12=draft}} from {{ill|Emperor Ninkō|ja|仁孝天皇|12=draft|12=draft}} onwards.

